    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair-condition driver that is usable as-is but shows its age. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear inside and out, including blemishes, tired trim, and other age-related imperfections, and it may need some maintenance or sorting depending on how picky you are. That said, it remains a straightforward, honest car for someone looking for an affordable entry point rather than a pristine example.",
