    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Rough, poor-condition car being sold honestly as-is. It has heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, with visible aging, blemishes, and signs of hard use, and it should be expected to need meaningful reconditioning and repairs. This is not a turn-key, clean example\u2014it\u2019s better suited for someone looking for a project, parts, or a very inexpensive vehicle to sort out. Buyers should expect flaws in appearance, deferred maintenance, and a generally tired overall presentation.",
