    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and wear, but it remains a practical option for someone who prioritizes price, utility, and potential. An honest, low-cost way to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 4950.0,
