      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout or a handy project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got a lot of honest value for someone who wants inexpensive wheels without spending a fortune. A great fit for a first-time driver, commuter, or anyone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of cosmetic wear in exchange for a very approachable price. If you want simple, budget-friendly transport with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running budget driver/project with a willing engine, dependable transmission operation, and a chassis that still feels serviceable on the road. This car shows its age cosmetically and will need attention in spots, but the core mechanical package is there, making it a great candidate for a commuter, backup car, or weekend revive. Starts, moves, and delivers honest, usable transportation with plenty of upside for someone who knows their way around maintenance.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest used car with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast at a strong value.",
